imit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjExMjc5NDk3NDE5MzAyODcx/mother-science.jpg 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjExMjc5NDk3NDE5MzAyODcx/mother-science.jpg 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjExMjc5NDk3NDE5MzAyODcx/mother-science.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"mother-science\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjExMjc5NDk3NDE5MzAyODcx/mother-science.jpg\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjExMjc5NDk3NDE5MzAyODcx/mother-science.jpg\" height=\"7334\" width=\"5500\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Courtesy of Mother Science\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/brand-bio\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eBrand Bio\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cem\u003e is Fashionista\u0026#39;s guide to the best independent fashion and \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/beauty\"\u003ebeauty\u003c/a\u003e brands — a resource for retailers, job seekers, B2B companies and consumers alike. If you\u0026#39;d like your brand to be featured, \u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/page/brand-form\"\u003efill out this form\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://share.hsforms.com/1CifB04FtQbK_suJ6ki-Vogs25du?__hstc=192178613.a94794eee9669159b9b5e1bff104317b.1725575872011.1733328254641.1733332907491.185\u0026amp;__hssc=192178613.5.1733332907491\u0026amp;__hsfp=1728485645\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMother Science\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eHeadquarters: Santa Monica, CA\u003cbr/\u003eE-commerce: \u003ca href=\"http://www.motherscience.com\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emotherscience.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eSocial Media: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/motherscience/?hl=en\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@motherscience\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTikTok\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat:\u003c/strong\u003e A \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin-care\u003c/a\u003e brand founded in 2023 that boasts a \u0026#34;small but mighty\u0026#34; product range.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range:\u003c/strong\u003e $89-$185\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounders: \u003c/strong\u003eAnn Marie Simpson-Einziger, Mike Einziger and Edna Coryell\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story: \u003c/strong\u003eMother Science was founded by Mike Einziger, lead guitarist of Incubus, and renowned violinist, Ann Marie Simpson-Einziger. In 2016, while on tour, Ann Marie developed tinea versicolor, a harmless skin condition that caused lightened patches of skin on her back. She wondered if there was some insight that could be used intentionally to reduce the look of dark spots on the skin. The couple assembled a team of leading scientists and, through their research, identified malassezin, a naturally occurring molecule found on skin with \u0026#34;dramatic skin health benefits,\u0026#34; including powerful results for dark spot reduction, brightening, smoothing and minimizing the look of lines and wrinkles, per the brand.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eMother Science is the only brand that uses this ingredient. The brand studied it on ex-vivo human skin, analyzing the expression of 22,000-plus genes per sample, over hundreds of samples, giving a deep knowledge of how the ingredient works on the skin. Mother Science has published scientific papers on malassezin in three dermatology journals. The brand\u0026#39;s groundbreaking clinical research on the novel use of malassezin in \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin care\u003c/a\u003e has been presented to 50,000-plus dermatologists at numerous dermatology conferences over the past three years.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHero Products:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com?id=133023X1595699\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fmotherscience.com%2Fcollections%2Fshop-all%2Fproducts%2Fretinol-synergist\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRetinol Synergist\u003c/a\u003e ($96), \u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/3CWhRnH\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMolecular Hero Serum\u003c/a\u003e ($89)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePR Representation:\u003c/strong\u003e Lisa Lauri Communications\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to get in touch: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://motherscience.com/pages/contact\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eContact form\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWant your brand featured? Hit the link below.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cf